{"tid":502841,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過細個發生咗啲事 屋企人係都唔信你？","createTime":"2017-12-18T09:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T13:30:47.000Z","uid":143699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"24a7576fb34c307c6fa0ddc22cc4eebc9c5b9b08","tid":502841,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"細個係幼稚園比人偷咗筒糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲要知道係邊個偷咗。點知老母唔信我，以為小朋友玩野。果陣嬲到pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走果陣仲要見到條友串77咗食緊我筒糖，差啲衝上去打7佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6788668c6d0baec4dc8fe24c72262616e6c6c4be","tid":502841,"uid":31181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"以家我廿幾歲仔 佢都信外人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74880c15868ed3355129d2aebbed34b23a2880e5","tid":502841,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T10:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以家我廿幾歲仔 佢都信外人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時咁樣真係會好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2b5d1dd198f218bbe09758615d657ee0d15304","tid":502841,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c7cb2e25d258e2be1fbdace59a2f7c3fc1e30f9","tid":502841,"uid":146170,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e8caf487305e0aa250026fc5c4d377af41661cf","tid":502841,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有晚係呀婆屋企見到窗外面有火車係天上面行緊,架火車仲要有燈閃閃下,見到入面有好多影,好似好多人係入面咁,我好肯定唔係發緊夢,但一直無人信我</blockquote><br />\n我信你！"},{"pid":"a5de4889bd673107baf1c976341ae88cb35e502a","tid":502841,"uid":14369